snp5.9:1.1_0: “Those in the past I used to be anointed
snp5.9:2.2_0: the sage has laid down craving;
snp5.9:2.4_0: crosses over clinging to the world.”
snp5.9:3.3_0: The desire for greed and desire
snp5.9:4.1_0: Those who have fully understood the mindful,
snp5.9:4.2_0: in the midst of the Dhamma,
snp5.9:4.4_0: has crossed over clinging to the world.”
